

A simple example. You do not need to have the system installed
to try it, just compile the library and example. Then invoke the
./run.sh script.

Content:

  simple-example.c   - source for application using the API
  simple-example     - executable
  run.sh             - wrapper to run the system without
                       installing library or server
  idsa.d/example     - fallback configuration file containing
                       rules
  
